# Example: RAG System Architecture

> Reference architecture diagram for a retrieval augmented generation system.
> Source template for [Mermaid conventions](../../meta/mermaid-conventions.md).

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Ingestion Pipeline"
        DOC[Documents] --> LOAD[Document Loader]
        LOAD --> CHUNK[Text Chunker]
        CHUNK --> EMBED[Embedding Model]
    end

    subgraph "Storage"
        EMBED --> VDB[(Vector Database)]
        EMBED --> META[(Metadata DB)]
    end

    subgraph "Query Pipeline"
        QUERY[User Query] --> QEMBED[Query Embedding]
        QEMBED --> RETRIEVE[Retriever]
        RETRIEVE --> VDB
        RETRIEVE --> RERANK[Reranker]
        RERANK --> AUGMENT[Prompt Augmentation]
        AUGMENT --> LLM[LLM]
        LLM --> RESPONSE[Response]
    end

    subgraph "Observability"
        LLM --> TRACE[Tracing]
        RETRIEVE --> TRACE
        TRACE --> METRICS[Metrics Dashboard]
    end
```
